Package: likelihoodExplore
Type: Package
Title: Likelihood Exploration
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Ben", "Barnard", email = "ben_barnard@baylor.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Maintainer: Ben Barnard <ben_barnard@baylor.edu>
Description: A package of likelihood functions and a function that creates 
    likelihood functions from density functions. The functions are meant to aid 
    in education of likelihood based methods. Included shiny app leverages 
    likelihood functions to explore likelihood based methods.
License: GPL-2
LazyData: TRUE
